<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>NERIVA - Programa de Referidos</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://i.postimg.cc/gjz4jfm1/Neriva-Logo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="shared.css">
    <style>
        /* ── PAGE HERO ── */
        .page-hero {
            padding: 3rem 5% 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% -10%, #0b2b0b 0%, #000 60%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .page-hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(0,255,65,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,65,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 20%, transparent 70%);
            -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 20%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .page-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        .page-hero-eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: rgba(0,255,65,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.25);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.62rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--green);
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }
        .page-hero-eyebrow::before { content:''; width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--green); animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse-dot { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1);}50%{opacity:0.4;transform:scale(0.7);} }
        .page-hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 7vw, 2.8rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, var(--green) 60%, #00aa22 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: clamp(1px, 1.5vw, 4px);
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .page-hero p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }
        .page-hero p strong { color: var(--green); }

        /* ── STATS ── */
        .ref-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .ref-stat { text-align: center; }
        .ref-stat-num { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 900; color: var(--green); line-height: 1; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,65,0.3); }
        .ref-stat-label { font-size: 0.65rem; color: #555; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 0.3rem; }

        /* ── MAIN SECTION ── */
        .ref-main { padding: 2.5rem 4%; }
        .ref-inner { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }

        /* ── PASOS ── */
        .ref-pasos-section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
        .ref-pasos-title {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--green);
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }
        .ref-pasos-title::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,65,0.4), transparent); }

        .ref-pasos-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 0.7rem;
        }
        @media (min-width: 600px) { .ref-pasos-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; } }

        .paso {
            background: rgba(0,255,65,0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.12);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.2rem 1rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
            transition: border-color 0.25s, background 0.25s;
        }
        .paso:hover { border-color: rgba(0,255,65,0.3); background: rgba(0,255,65,0.05); }
        @media (min-width: 600px) { .paso { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; gap: 0; } }

        .paso-num {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--green);
            opacity: 0.25;
            line-height: 1;
            min-width: 2.5rem;
        }
        @media (min-width: 600px) { .paso-num { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; min-width: unset; } }

        .paso-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: none; }
        @media (min-width: 600px) { .paso-icon { display: block; } }

        .paso-text h4 { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ddd; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .paso-text p { font-size: 0.73rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; }
        @media (min-width: 600px) { .paso-text h4 { text-align: center; } .paso-text p { text-align: center; } }

        /* ── REF BOX ── */
        .ref-box-wrapper { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .ref-box {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0d0d0d, #080808);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .ref-box::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--green), transparent);
            opacity: 0.4;
        }
        .ref-crear { text-align: center; }
        .ref-crear > p { color: #777; font-size: 0.82rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.7; }
        .ref-crear-label {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--green);
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }
        .ref-input-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
        }
        @media (min-width: 500px) { .ref-input-row { flex-direction: row; } }

        .ref-input {
            flex: 1;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.25);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .ref-input::placeholder { color: #444; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: none; }
        .ref-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,255,65,0.15); background: rgba(0,255,65,0.04); }
        .ref-input.error { border-color: var(--red); animation: shake 0.35s ease; }
        @keyframes shake { 0%,100%{transform:translateX(0);}25%{transform:translateX(-6px);}75%{transform:translateX(6px);} }

        .ref-error-msg { color: var(--red); font-size: 0.72rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; }

        .btn-crear-codigo {
            background: var(--green);
            color: #000;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            white-space: nowrap;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,255,65,0.2);
            width: 100%;
        }
        @media (min-width: 500px) { .btn-crear-codigo { width: auto; } }
        .btn-crear-codigo:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
        .btn-crear-codigo:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }
        .btn-crear-codigo:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,255,65,0.4); }

        /* Estado activo */
        .ref-activo { display: none; }
        .ref-activo-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.6rem; }
        .ref-activo-header h3 { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 1.5px; }
        .ref-cambiar { background: none; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: #666; padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 3px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.7rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .ref-cambiar:hover { color: #fff; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

        .ref-link-display {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.2);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .ref-link-url {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: var(--green);
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            word-break: break-all;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .btn-copiar {
            width: 100%;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.4);
            color: var(--green);
            padding: 0.55rem 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-copiar:hover { background: rgba(0,255,65,0.08); }
        .btn-copiar:active, .btn-copiar.copiado { background: var(--green); color: #000; }

        .ref-compartir { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 0.8rem; }
        .ref-compartir > p { width: 100%; color: #444; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.1rem; }
        .btn-share { flex: 1; min-width: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.35rem; padding: 0.7rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.74rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; border: none; transition: all 0.2s; text-decoration: none; }
        .btn-share:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
        .btn-share-wa { background: rgba(37,211,102,0.1); color: #25d366; border: 1px solid rgba(37,211,102,0.3); }
        .btn-share-wa:hover { background: rgba(37,211,102,0.18); }
        .btn-share-ig { background: rgba(225,48,108,0.07); color: #e1306c; border: 1px solid rgba(225,48,108,0.25); }
        .btn-share-copy { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color: #aaa; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }

        /* ── BENEFICIOS ── */
        .ref-beneficios { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .beneficios-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.7rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        @media (min-width: 600px) { .beneficios-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 1rem; } }
        .beneficio-card {
            background: rgba(0,255,65,0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.1);
            border-radius: 7px;
            padding: 1.1rem 0.9rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: border-color 0.25s, background 0.25s;
        }
        .beneficio-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,255,65,0.3); background: rgba(0,255,65,0.06); }
        .beneficio-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .beneficio-title { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: #ddd; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
        .beneficio-desc { font-size: 0.68rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; }

        /* ── FAQ ── */
        .ref-faq { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .faq-list { margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
        .faq-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .faq-question {
            width: 100%;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .faq-question:hover { color: var(--green); }
        .faq-arrow { font-size: 0.7rem; transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .faq-item.open .faq-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }
        .faq-answer { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.35s ease; }
        .faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 200px; }
        .faq-answer p { padding: 0 1rem 1rem; color: #666; font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.7; }

        /* ── CTA FOOTER ── */
        .ref-cta-bottom {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0d0d0d, #080808);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.15);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .ref-cta-bottom h3 { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 3vw, 1.3rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .ref-cta-bottom p { color: #666; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        .btn-wa-bottom { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: rgba(37,211,102,0.1); border: 1.5px solid rgba(37,211,102,0.35); color: #25d366; padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.82rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .btn-wa-bottom:hover { background: rgba(37,211,102,0.18); }

        /* ── BANNER REFERIDO ── */
        .ref-banner { display: none; position: fixed; bottom: 1rem; left: 1rem; right: 1rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1f0d, #050f05); border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem 0.9rem 1.2rem; z-index: 3000; box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,255,65,0.25); text-align: center; }
        @media (min-width: 500px) { .ref-banner { left: 50%; right: auto; transform: translateX(-50%); width: auto; min-width: 250px; max-width: 85vw; } }
        .ref-banner.visible { display: block; animation: bannerIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); }
        @keyframes bannerIn { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);} }
        .ref-banner > p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
        .ref-banner strong { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .ref-banner-close { position: absolute; top: 0.5rem; right: 0.6rem; background: none; border: none; color: #555; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <a href="index.html" class="header-logo">NERIVA</a>
    <nav class="header-nav">
        <a href="index.html" class="header-nav-link">🛍️ Tienda</a>
        <a href="referidos.html" class="header-nav-link active">🔗 Referidos</a>
        <a href="revendedores.html" class="header-nav-link">💰 Revendé</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/5491128330853" target="_blank" class="header-nav-link wa">💬 WA</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content reveal">
        <div class="page-hero-eyebrow">Programa de referidos</div>
        <h1>Referí y<br>ganá descuentos</h1>
        <p>Compartí tu link con amigos. Cuando alguien compre con tu código, te damos un <strong>descuento en tu próxima compra</strong>.</p>
        <div class="ref-stats">
            <div class="ref-stat">
                <div class="ref-stat-num">0%</div>
                <div class="ref-stat-label">Costo de entrada</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ref-stat">
                <div class="ref-stat-num">∞</div>
                <div class="ref-stat-label">Límite de referidos</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ref-stat">
                <div class="ref-stat-num">+%</div>
                <div class="ref-stat-label">Descuento garantizado</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN -->
<section class="ref-main">
    <div class="ref-inner">

        <!-- PASOS -->
        <div class="ref-pasos-section reveal">
            <h2 class="ref-pasos-title">Cómo funciona</h2>
            <div class="ref-pasos-grid">
                <div class="paso">
                    <div class="paso-num">01</div>
                    <div class="paso-icon">🔑</div>
                    <div class="paso-text">
                        <h4>Creá tu código</h4>
                        <p>Elegí un nombre o apodo único. Solo letras y números.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="paso">
                    <div class="paso-num">02</div>
                    <div class="paso-icon">📲</div>
                    <div class="paso-text">
                        <h4>Compartilo</h4>
                        <p>Mandalo por WhatsApp, Instagram, o donde quieras.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="paso">
                    <div class="paso-num">03</div>
                    <div class="paso-icon">🎁</div>
                    <div class="paso-text">
                        <h4>Ganá descuento</h4>
                        <p>Cuando tu amigo compre usando tu código, te avisamos y te damos el descuento.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- REF BOX -->
        <div class="ref-box-wrapper reveal">
            <div class="ref-box">
                <div class="ref-crear" id="refCrear">
                    <span class="ref-crear-label">Tu código personalizado</span>
                    <p>Elegí un nombre único para identificarte. Solo letras y números, sin espacios.</p>
                    <div class="ref-input-row">
                        <input type="text" class="ref-input" id="refInput" placeholder="Ej: MARIA, JUAN23..." maxlength="16" autocomplete="off">
                        <button class="btn-crear-codigo" id="btnCrearCodigo" onclick="crearCodigo()">Crear código</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ref-error-msg" id="refError"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="ref-activo" id="refActivo">
                    <div class="ref-activo-header">
                        <h3 id="refCodigoLabel">TU CÓDIGO: -</h3>
                        <button class="ref-cambiar" onclick="cambiarCodigo()">Cambiar código</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ref-link-display">
                        <span class="ref-link-url" id="refLinkDisplay">-</span>
                        <button class="btn-copiar" id="btnCopiarLink" onclick="copiarLink()">📋 Copiar link</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ref-compartir">
                        <p>Compartir directo:</p>
                        <button class="btn-share btn-share-wa" onclick="shareWhatsapp()">💬 WhatsApp</button>
                        <button class="btn-share btn-share-ig" onclick="shareInstagram()">📸 Instagram</button>
                        <button class="btn-share btn-share-copy" onclick="copiarLink()">📋 Copiar</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BENEFICIOS -->
        <div class="ref-beneficios reveal">
            <h2 class="ref-pasos-title">Beneficios</h2>
            <div class="beneficios-grid">
                <div class="beneficio-card">
                    <div class="beneficio-icon">💸</div>
                    <div class="beneficio-title">Descuento real</div>
                    <p class="beneficio-desc">Cada referido exitoso te suma descuento en tu próxima compra.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="beneficio-card">
                    <div class="beneficio-icon">♾️</div>
                    <div class="beneficio-title">Sin límite</div>
                    <p class="beneficio-desc">Podés referir a todas las personas que quieras.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="beneficio-card">
                    <div class="beneficio-icon">⚡</div>
                    <div class="beneficio-title">Instantáneo</div>
                    <p class="beneficio-desc">Creás tu código en segundos y empezás a compartir.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="beneficio-card">
                    <div class="beneficio-icon">🤝</div>
                    <div class="beneficio-title">Tu amigo también gana</div>
                    <p class="beneficio-desc">Los que usan tu link también pueden acceder a beneficios.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <div class="ref-faq reveal">
            <h2 class="ref-pasos-title">Preguntas frecuentes</h2>
            <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        ¿Cómo sé si alguien usó mi código?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Te avisamos por WhatsApp cuando alguien realice una compra usando tu código. Coordinamos el descuento en tu próxima compra directamente.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        ¿Cuánto es el descuento?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>El descuento varía según la compra realizada por tu referido. Consultanos por WhatsApp para más detalles sobre los beneficios actuales.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        ¿Mi código tiene vencimiento?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>No, tu código se guarda en tu dispositivo y no tiene vencimiento. Podés seguir compartiéndolo cuando quieras.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        ¿Qué pasa si cambio de dispositivo?
                        <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
